                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.348 Z 4/52: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Portugal</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dearing</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lisbon</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-10-16T11:00:00+00:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 16, 1923—11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received 7:35 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>63. Department’s instruction of September 18th. Portuguese Government authorizes
                    flight of <hi rend="italic">ZR–3</hi> across Portugal and Azores.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dearing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
